videos.description: Drew Peterson dishes it to Boogie Ellis for the 3-pointer to give the Trojans the lead.
videos.headline: Boogie Ellis pulls up and knocks down the 3 for USC

videos.description: Quincy Guerrier doesn't give up on the play and slams home the rock to pull the Ducks within one.
videos.headline: Quincy Guerrier's second effort pays off for an Oregon slam

videos.description: Drew Peterson fakes out two defenders and knocks down the and-1 to extend the Trojans' lead.
videos.headline: Drew Peterson is smooth as silk as he drains the and-1 for USC

videos.description: Eric Williams Jr. jumps out of the gym as he throws down the lob from De'Vion Harmon to pull the Ducks closer.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (De'vion Harmon slams it home with authority) 2022/02/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Eric Williams launches from the hardwood to throw down the alley-oop

videos.description: Isaiah Mobley is 'cooler than the other side of the pillow' as he drains the smooth and-1.
videos.headline: Isaiah Mobley with the smooth and-1 bucket for USC

videos.description: Reese Dixon-Waters gathers the dime from Ethan Anderson and throws it down to regain the lead late in the second half.
videos.headline: Ethan Anderson with the absolute dime to Reese Dixon for a USC flush

videos.description: Jacob Young pulls and knocks down the 3-pointer to give the Ducks the lead late in the second half.
videos.headline: Jacob Young buries the clutch 3 to take the lead for Oregon
